derexsv.ppf.command.ensure_teleports.des:
Secures PPF teleporters.
Use: ppf.ensure-teleports all|here|farm|ppf|<LocationName>
  all  = all PPF_* and Farm
  here = only in the current location
  farm = only on the main Farm
  ppf  = only in PPF_* (all)
  <LocationName> = exact name of a location
derexsv.ppf.command.clean.description:
Cleans debris/grass/trees/farm resources (PPF Clean Helper).
Use: ppf.clean here|all|ppf
derexsv.ppf.command.strip.description:
Removes vanilla buildings in PPF_* (Farmhouse always, Greenhouse if broken).
Use: ppf.strip here|all
